{"title":"保定三题","authors":["田间"],"dates":[{"year":1978,"month":2,"day":23}],"parts":[{"type":"paragraph","text":"保定三题"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"田间"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"途中"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"雪中红叶未凋零，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"枝枝招展向晴空。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"墙上新画红艳艳，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"天翻地覆音铮铮。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"试问恶鬼今何在？"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"除恶务尽斩毒根。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"麦田青青一层层，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"雪未尽时春已临。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"春在人心发绿芽，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"古城道上铁牛奔。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"古城换了一幅景，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"精神抖擞战鬼神。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"重来保定"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"巍巍一座古城，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"谁敢化为刀林。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"昔日枪声在耳，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"山间硝烟未尽。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"青山松枝不断，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"敢和乌云抗争。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"莲池灯火未熄，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"映照战士丹心。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"人民何畏小虫，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"仰望旭日东升。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"挥手高歌华主席，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"喜雪飘飘正来临。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"余毒必将荡涤尽，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"不久红花满乾坤！"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"吟雪"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"今日重来古战场，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"往日血汗怎能忘？"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"往日春风怎能忘？"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"往日野火怎能忘？"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"奸贼磨刀刀已折，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"白雪皑皑见银装。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"明镜常在英雄掌，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"罪恶黑手难巧妆。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"明镜常照革命者，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"两面派们也是狼。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"“女皇”小照早撕碎，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"一枕黄粱枉断肠。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"需知——雪中红梅枝更壮。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"需知——雪后更喜红太阳。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"需知——雪后百鸟更翱翔。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"今日雪中千里行，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"春来再看换新妆。"}],"comments":[],"comment_pivots":[],"description":"","page_start":4,"page_end":4}